lead_paragraph: Longtime rivals Ryan Lochte and Michael Phelps set up their lone showdown at the U.S. Olympic swimming trials by qualifying first and second in the 200-meter individual medley Thursday.

headline.main: Lochte, Phelps Set Up Lone Showdown at US Olympic Trials
